<section>
	<h2>Configuration options</h2>
	<table class="table">
		<thead>
			<tr>
				<th>Option</th>
				<th>Description</th>
				<th>How to configure</th>
				<th>Values</th>
			</tr>
		</thead>
		<tbody>
			<tr>
				<td><code>value</code></td>
				<td>Represents the progress of the task.</td>
				<td>Add the <code>value</code> attribute to the progress element. If <code>value</code> is omitted, the progress bar is considered to be indeterminate, which means that there is no indication on the actual progress of the task.</td>
				<td>
					<dl>
						<dt>Decimal number:</dt>
						<dd>Current progress of the task. Must be a decimal number between 0 and the <code>max</code> value.</dd>
					</dl>
				</td>
			</tr>
		</tbody>
	</table>
</section>

